  <metadata>
    <name>INN-L3 — Zillertal Alps Weekend Loop</name>
    <desc>Deploy from INN and ride into the Zillertal Alps. Hit Gerlos Pass — 1507m and Zillertaler Höhenstrasse — 2020m. Loop back to INN over a packed 2–3 day weekend escape. No highways, just curves and elevation.</desc>
    <author><name>JetMyMoto</name></author>
    <time>2026-04-08T07:39:08.207Z</time>
  </metadata>
